{"tid":1646534,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"義士被殺 我地全部都係幫兇 都有責任","createTime":"2019-10-11T10:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T02:07:19.000Z","uid":287032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d6d3aae6beb75c71f7565acad9a84e6be1516170","tid":1646534,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:37:30.000Z","msg":"點解？<br />\n因為我地無做到救人<br />\n臨場只係識逃走<br />\n眼白白睇住手足被狗捉<br />\n之後折磨...酷刑...被殺...棄屍<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">不被捕<br />\n齊上齊落<br />\n一個都不能少</span><br />\n<br />\n唔係口號<br />\n而係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">行動</span></span><br />\n<br />\n比狗撲低既手足<br />\n請記住<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你要用一生既氣力反抗<br />\n否則你唔會再有機會反抗<br />\n因為可能會被殺</span><br />\n<br />\n記住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打狗<br />\n還拖<br />\n救人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n生存與死亡<br />\n一直控制係大家手上"},{"pid":"96db13a790d73c96a1fc6cdfadfe5ce3977332ff","tid":1646534,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:38:02.000Z","msg":"救人"},{"pid":"9fd607a636e07084171c26eb98e13bd034a33027","tid":1646534,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:38:16.000Z","msg":"救人"},{"pid":"e85706426e5125a55f49366649b8749dabbf8bb2","tid":1646534,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:38:40.000Z","msg":"打狗 救人"},{"pid":"f5d6e2a8a388be1aa6d097f2694418db0263da79","tid":1646534,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:39:15.000Z","msg":"就算平時所謂蒙面法而拘捕既<br />\n都要救"},{"pid":"0b640a99d4cd0e7f1b98829402c138e25dfe8f99","tid":1646534,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5d6e2a8a388be1aa6d097f2694418db0263da79","tid":1646534,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:39:15.000Z","msg":"就算平時所謂蒙面法而拘捕既<br />\n都要救"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:39:32.000